Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.55,0:01:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, a roller coaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.61,0:01:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.38,0:01:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Coward! Chicken! {actually "caterpillar" - 泣き虫 毛虫 挟んで 捨てろ: Crybaby, caterpillar, pick it up and throw it away}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.22,0:01:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She was stung and she was bitten! 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.78,0:01:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sniff... {https://jisho.org/word/%E3%81%8F%E3%81%99%E3%82%93 - because she's about to cry}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.86,0:01:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not {\i1}that{\i0} scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.64,0:01:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.44,0:01:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.29,0:02:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It actually wasn't {\i1}that{\i0} scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.80,0:02:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.70,0:02:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're great!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.03,0:02:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Tsuneko?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.24,0:03:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If Nono-chan can ride it just fine, \Nwhy wouldn't I be fine too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.50,0:03:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna ride an even scarier one!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.05,0:03:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Whew, that was scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.22,0:03:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.15,0:03:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough for me. \NI'm feeling sick. {lit: drunk [with motion sickness]}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.05,0:03:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.31,0:03:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsuneko-chan, didn't you shriek on this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.45,0:03:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.67,0:03:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just ya-w-ning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's ride the {\i1}Fighting Pirates{\i0} next!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.76,0:03:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.26,0:03:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.55,0:04:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are no good! {/embarrassing}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.01,0:04:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go by ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.47,0:04:08.61,Thought,,0,0,0,,What now? \NI mustn’t let myself scream again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.58,0:04:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm starving.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.87,0:04:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. \NLet's grab something to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.48,0:05:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.62,0:05:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,In your dreams! {/I'll eat}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're done, \Nlet's hit the star attraction. {idk what's honmei here, doesn't seem to connect in any way to the den den screw we see next}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.19,0:05:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll ride it! \NI feel that I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.16,0:05:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.00,0:05:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsuneko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.77,0:05:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.86,0:05:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm good! \NLet's get in already.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That was so fun! \NTsuneko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.93,0:06:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't even feel it. {lit: because I'm unconcerned (about); unbothered; unworried; nonchalant; not caring; not minding - could switch to "not a coward"}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.63,0:06:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll ride it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.89,0:06:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome! \NShe let go of her hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.61,0:07:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsunta-kun... is actually a punk! {as in music and fashion I guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.72,0:07:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Our reserved Tsunta-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.40,0:07:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't no way! {could be "just kidding" but more likely that's what tsunta claims himself but this kid doubts it}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.31,0:07:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He's so quiet all the time. {lit: everyone is so quiet - ???, could be "you were silent so I decided to start a convo somehow"}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.78,0:07:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,For a moment there,\N I thought it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.69,0:07:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But his hairstyle is normal. {lit: hairdo is hairdo - ???}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.91,0:07:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo's sporting a London-style bob.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.07,0:07:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But Tsunta's hairdo is too plain. {same word as reserved before}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.07,0:07:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's a punk?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.27,0:07:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.69,0:07:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s annoying when a kid like that joins in—\Nshe doesn’t even know what a punk is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.02,0:08:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand \Nwhy you can't explain it! Tell me! {lit: I don't know where the lie is}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.38,0:08:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing’s more pathetic than trying to explain \Na lie someone tossed out as a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.09,0:08:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should I tell you if you're constantly teasing me? Aren't we enemies? {idk}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.28,0:08:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't that Tsunta-kun just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.36,0:08:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He ran over that way, \Nwearing sunglasses and a sleeveless shirt. {lit: torn to shreds t-shirt}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.19,0:08:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hah! She really did it.{idk}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.22,0:08:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ignorance is a scary thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.09,0:08:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You probably don't even realize that lie \Nyou just made up repeats what I've heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.38,0:08:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? When did I copy anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.25,0:08:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just what I said earlier, \Nthat Tsunta-kun is a punk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.42,0:08:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? So being a punk is about \Nwearing sunglasses and sleeveless shirts?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.05,0:08:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No, now that I think of it... {idk why he is confused here, she didn't say anything wrong}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.68,0:08:56.89,Thought,,0,0,0,,What is wrong with me, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.60,0:09:00.88,Thought,,0,0,0,,To think I'd forget my all-important abacus!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.36,0:09:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm positive it was Tsunta-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.38,0:09:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But Tsunta-kun should be \Nat his abacus class by now. {I promise it would make sense later}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.91,0:10:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Get seated already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.41,0:10:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.25,0:10:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If we take... {nc}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.61,0:10:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,185 yen, plus 125 yen,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.10,0:10:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,plus 820 yen, plus 821 yen,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.63,0:10:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,plus 119 yen, plus 780 yen... {actually not "plus" but "or" but they eventually do sum it so w/e}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.66,0:10:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsunta-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.56,0:10:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.15,0:10:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's 1,850 yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.37,0:10:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.84,0:10:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Michio-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.59,0:10:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's 2,850 yen
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Splendid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.47,0:10:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's try a double neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.24,0:11:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Tsunta-kun is so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.39,0:11:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,280 yen, 150 yen, 591 yen, \N356 yen, 305 yen, and 290 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.44,0:11:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ankichi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.56,0:11:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's 3,858 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.38,0:11:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Splendid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.65,0:11:20.62,Thought,,0,0,0,,Wrong again...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.44,0:11:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's reset.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.79,0:11:32.30,Thought,,0,0,0,,All I have is an abacus! {idk what he means}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.48,0:11:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsunta-kun threw his abacus. {/tossed}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.29,0:11:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.69,0:11:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He's so radical!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.78,0:11:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a true punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.06,0:12:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um, I mean... Uhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.60,0:12:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're that kid... \NWhat was it? Sakuramochi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.30,0:12:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakuramochi Ankichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:13:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy! I can't believe \Nyou even remembered me by my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.72,0:13:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, goodbye now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.19,0:13:37.17,Thought,,0,0,0,,I ended up catering to the public again... {lit: responded to everyone's expectations}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.86,0:13:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to be more frugal. {/cut down on it}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.91,0:13:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's walk one station.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.65,0:14:23.27,Thought,,0,0,0,,There was a girl who was put to sleep \Nevery night at 9 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.27,0:14:29.14,Thought,,0,0,0,,She was forced to sleep \Nat 9 o'clock sharp no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.14,0:14:33.05,Thought,,0,0,0,,There must be something interesting \Nhappening at night after 9 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.05,0:14:35.20,Thought,,0,0,0,,That's how she felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.56,0:14:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.73,0:14:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever stayed up late at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.59,0:15:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.18,0:15:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I sometimes stay up late to watch TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.69,0:15:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The shows they play at night \Nare way more fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.76,0:15:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.17,0:15:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm tellin' you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.48,0:15:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,midnight ramen is the best thing ever. {lit: ramen you eat in the middle of the night is the best}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.95,0:15:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, a beef bowl \Nalso tastes better at nighttime. {not sure what's that ma/a}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.82,0:15:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it about sorting books at night that causes night to turn into morning? {muzu's: Hear 夜本の整備とかしててつい朝になっちゃうとかいうこと何}{/Yuri, what is it about sorting books, \Nthat causes you to ending up reading all night? - nc what's that yasa, assuming it's something to do with night}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.54,0:15:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it’s true! I just start reading one \Nby accident and forget all about sorting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.50,0:15:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It happens to me too, whenever I try \Nto sort records. It really does!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.17,0:15:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.96,0:15:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, "I'm home!" Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.32,0:15:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.34,0:15:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Suneo, where's mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.24,0:15:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom went to visit our aunt in Yokohama \Nand will stay overnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.62,0:15:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,She told us two to watch over the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.19,0:16:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What about dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.36,0:16:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Went on a business trip. \NHe said he'll be back tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.78,0:16:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He told me to "Fully close the gas valve, \Nturn off all the lights, and go to bed at 9 o'clock."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.01,0:16:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooray! I'm staying up all night today!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.73,0:16:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you can't do that! {nc}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.50,0:16:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom wants us to go to sleep at 9. \NShe told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.50,0:16:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hm! }
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.15,0:16:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so daft, Suneo! {baka}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.32,0:16:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Staying up late is fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.80,0:16:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The ramen you eat at midnight \Nis a great deal tastier!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.03,0:16:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how to make ramen, sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.39,0:16:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.06,0:16:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You've never even made it before!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.00,0:16:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You make it. {nc}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.31,0:16:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.19,0:16:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.03,0:16:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're better with your hands than me. {/more adroit/skillful}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, what's for dinner today?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.87,0:16:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's shrimp gratin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.08,0:16:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so easygoing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.79,0:17:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to eat a lot to build up stamina \Nand stay up all night!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.03,0:17:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.16,0:17:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to sleep, Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.28,0:17:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget to do your dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.32,0:17:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I remember! \NThe night is long.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.65,0:17:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't know how to enjoy life. {unsure}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.77,0:17:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,How about sorting some books?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.17,0:18:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I have fewer books than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.52,0:18:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's sort the records too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.65,0:18:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They're even fewer than the books.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.06,0:18:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiriko-chan lied to me—\Nthis nighttime TV is totally boring!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.21,0:18:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe a ramen would cheer me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.40,0:18:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Suneo! Suneo!\N Make me some ramen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.40,0:19:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to tell mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.25,0:19:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.55,0:19:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't any better.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.63,0:19:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But now I’m stuffed and feel sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.16,0:19:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should’ve asked him \Nto make me a beef bowl…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.79,0:20:04.55,Thought,,0,0,0,,It's still only 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.88,0:20:09.19,Thought,,0,0,0,,Let's go to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.98,0:20:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Tsuneko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.69,0:20:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.41,0:20:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,When the night slips past 2 a.m.... {unsure what he means, [spirits come out]?}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.34,0:20:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Suneo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.59,0:20:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Suneo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.39,0:20:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I already made ramen for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.81,0:20:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.04,0:20:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.64,0:20:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you leave without me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.73,0:20:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll definitely tell mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.99,0:21:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,0)}Jeez! I'll never stay up late again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.82,0:21:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're gonna do it, do it alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.38,0:21:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,My favorite things...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.98,0:21:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ice cream! \NMy favorite things...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.13,0:21:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Chocolate! \NFavorite... Things...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.72,0:21:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Biscuits! \NFavorite things...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.02,0:21:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure is a pain... \NThat music homework they gave us today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.22,0:21:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a breeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.59,0:21:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Songwriting is easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.67,0:22:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's a strong statement to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.42,0:22:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's 'cause I do it all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.72,0:22:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.56,0:22:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You got a problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.26,0:22:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh? No, not at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.35,0:22:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You just need to let the song \Nflow naturally out of your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.50,0:22:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Just repeat after me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.40,0:22:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'm one of those people\Nthey call a natural musician. {lit: music people - isn't it that kind of thing?}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.36,0:22:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You got something to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.03,0:22:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's just too sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.29,0:22:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So how do you write lyrics and music?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.73,0:22:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,All at once! {/at the same time}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.77,0:22:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.50,0:22:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, when I get home...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.55,0:22:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We’re probably having \Nmy favorite for dinner, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.47,0:22:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you run around the house \Nat times like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.81,0:22:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should we?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.89,0:22:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,To work up an appetite, obviously!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.93,0:22:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,At times like that, \Na song comes out nice and easy...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.06,0:23:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, it's rice with curry! {karee raisu}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.84,0:23:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.65,0:23:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe curry rice would rhyme better? {karii raisu - basically the same thing as karee raisu but I don't see a way to convey such small nuance in english}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.00,0:23:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,"It's curry rice..."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.27,0:23:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, it's rice with curry! {still sings karee so idk, maybe a mistake since it's so insignificant, maybe she changed her mind; feel free to make this "curry rice"}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.21,0:23:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So it's a poem!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.88,0:23:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,My talent is almost frightening sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.29,0:23:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's for dinner today?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.20,0:23:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yakiniku. {/roasted meat; grill​}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.59,0:23:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yakiniku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.06,0:23:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be bass.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.60,0:23:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm tenor. {daddy sang bass, mama sang tenor, me and little brother would join right in there ♫}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.11,0:23:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yakiniku!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.18,0:23:43.39,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Yakiniku!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.55,0:23:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother is bass.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.24,0:23:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Michiko is tenor.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.93,0:23:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yakiniku...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.94,0:23:51.58,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Yakiniku...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.00,0:24:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{can't make out any words, most likely gibberish}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.08,0:24:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsunta, go buy some eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.44,0:24:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.10,0:24:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{could be italian but most likely gibberish too}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.78,0:24:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.31,0:24:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, teacher, \Nwhere is the song supposed to start?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.53,0:24:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.04,0:24:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't have you lose \Nto your peasant friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.66,0:24:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Brazil, Brazil, they have samba. {spelled "sanba"}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.26,0:24:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll get to eat a juicy mango? {lit: Maybe today's side dish is saury? (spelled "sanma"); I couldn't think of a food that properly rhymes with samba, let alone a fish}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.85,0:24:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This smell...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.33,0:24:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an onion!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.71,0:25:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't matter if you hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.38,0:25:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to eat onions to grow smarter.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.11,0:25:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to write a song.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.04,0:25:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,On-on-onion... {lit: ball, ball, onion}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.19,0:25:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ion...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.58,0:25:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand that smell!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.80,0:25:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If Tsuneko can do it, \Nthere's no way I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.01,0:25:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have to think of it as an onion.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.58,0:25:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Imagine... Imagine...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.62,0:25:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That it's a chestnut! {amaguri = broiled sweet chestnuts​}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.36,0:25:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's better. {nc}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.23,0:25:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Chestnuts​, chestnuts, \Nchestnuts, chestnuts,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.41,0:25:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,chest...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.38,0:26:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's onions!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.76,0:26:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No good.\NI can't make a song.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.04,0:26:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.84,0:26:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You finished your song?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.22,0:26:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Omelet today...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.41,0:26:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Red ketchup!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.45,0:26:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.45,0:26:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.13,0:26:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hya! Omelet today!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.01,0:27:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,With the yellow of the egg! {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.77,0:27:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Mi-Mi-Mix it with flour! {same}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.53,0:27:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hamburger, hamburger.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.56,0:27:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Woohoo! Another great song \Nis already coming along!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.81,0:27:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.28,0:27:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I love hamburgers.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.45,0:27:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I like hamburgers too. {prolly means "as well as curry rice"}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.08,0:27:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're happy together—
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.26,0:27:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,me and hamburger!
